{"tid":1204331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"廣傳 因金鐘出閘比狗逗，見唔到老豆最後一面","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T00:25:36.000Z","uid":166085,"like":3081,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4365c44acb6fc06d1cb4e6da398cdac35d24df","tid":1204331,"uid":166085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n今日放工前收到老母whatsapp，<br />\n話我知老豆就唔掂，<br />\n叫我盡快收工趕返屋企，<br />\n咁我就拿拿淋做完野，咩個背囊就9秒9衝返歸啦，<br />\n我都知今晚港島區戒嚴咁，<br />\n但我心諗我正常市民，唔會關我事既，<br />\n點知一出閘就比班警犬截住，話我有可疑，<br />\n之後叫我泊埋牆搜身，我即刻同佢講我老豆就死，<br />\n趕住返屋企見佢最後一面，<br />\n點知佢地唔聽不特止，仲同我講會慢慢搜。<br />\n我同班後生仔一企就企左大半個鐘，<br />\n我係咁求佢地快d得唔得，完全無理過我，<br />\n最後好似有幾個議員黎幫我地先走到。<br />\n<br />\n但所到屋企老豆已經唔得，去緊醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解警察明明幫市民，點解唔幫下我老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心情沉重，唔作回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cce146845b2b850169ae25b35a0d8ca850d901","tid":1204331,"uid":103759,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ArmChannelTV/videos/449075855872630/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FArmChannelTV%2Fvideos%2F449075855872630%2F&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiWsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=208972fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ArmChannelTV/videos/449075855872630/</a>"},{"pid":"7876621faefd26e4b36e3d66ae4e70da45ab7a2c","tid":1204331,"uid":138658,"like":321,"dislike":1,"score":320,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"警犬正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f1015a85305ae6496c9df2e89efa361a8234c8","tid":1204331,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:54:11.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"e2757ddd11e2a2e857b5c0bd9927a60